# --- Rust Recursive Ignores ---
# Ignores all compiled artifacts and build folders
**/target/

# --- Cargo Specific ---
# Contains your local registry and crates (usually not needed in repo)
**/*.rs.bk
**/cargo-bench.timestamp

# --- IDE & OS Specific ---
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/.DS_Store
**/*.user
Thumbs.db

# --- Logs & Temp ---
*.log
**/tmp/

# --- Development Config ---
# For environment variables
**/.env
**/.env.local
